bugs
----

- safes, cages, and diamonds can be drawn on the outer perimeter when they're used to plug
  gaps in extra walls

- spirits can somehow run down their deltas outside of the update loop, so they freeze.
  - might the delta <= 0 check in drawloop - possibly fixed. leave this here and see if it re-occurs

game features
-------------

- structured earth 
  - fill interior with rectangles and remove straight lines
  - convert earth to boulders and diamonds
- structures
  - safe room
    - turn a diamond into a safe
	- draw a wall box so that the new safe is on one side
	- fill with diamonds
  - extra walls get curvy corners
  - brackets - C, L or U shaped structures with curvy corners - done in special brick like Repton polkas
  - safes and cages in extra walls
- finish a level
- boulderUpdate flag which triggers 
  - when bob moves a boulder
  - when bob digs earth, diamonds, keys
  - keys open safes
  - spirits enter cages
  - a boulder falls
- v2 map builder
  - random WxH box filled with stuff
  - has a random exit
  - a tunnel of random length
  - then another WxH random box

