programming
-----------

- maps aren't very good when they're narrow
- pushing might be improved by animating bob and then moving the boulder on 3/4ths of his delta
- collision detection might be improved by looking at deltas to gauge distance
- css class should be property of the map[][] entity
- comments
- probably more than a few places to optimise
- restructure where it makes sense
- varieties of earth
- tools to ...
  - build level JSON from flat files
- swipe gestures to play on mobile
- versions
- repair all the JSON stuff and make it more dynamic (and parseable)

